{
  "id": "f04r",
  "recto_verso": "recto",
  "gathering_position": 4,
  "damage": "water_damage_moderate",
  "hand_notes": "hand appears more pressured here, several strokes heavier than surrounding pages",
  "section_breaks": [1],
  "vellum_stock": "standard",
  "lines": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "nit übel nehmen. Er hat es selber getan.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Nun muß ich von dem fehler reden, vnd das ist das schwerste",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "in disem gantzen buch. Ich hab ihn lang hinausgeschodben.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Er iß nun da. Ich muß ihn sagen.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.98}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "In dem dritten Psalter, den ich schrib, — es war im herbst",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "des jares MCCCCLV — da habe ich einen fehler gemacht.",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Nit einen kleinen fehler in einem unwichtigen wort.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Einen fehler in dem achtzehnden Psalm, in dem vers, der",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "spricht: caeli enarrant gloriam Dei. Die himmel erzählen",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "die ehre Gottes. Ich schrib: caeli narrant — ohne das",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "e, ohne das enarrare, das erzählen-von-anfang-bis-ende.",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "Nur narrant. Nur sagen. Das ist ein kleines e, das fehlt.",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "Aber in dem Psalm ist es nit ein kleines e. Es ist der",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "unterschied zwischen dem sagen vnd dem auseinandersetzen,",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "zwischen dem hinweisen vnd dem vollständigen zeugnis.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Vnd ich hab es erst gemerkt, do das buch schon gebunden",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "war vnd zu den brüdern gegangen war, die es bestellt hatten.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Ich hab es gemerkt, do ich in meiner zelle saß vnd in",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "dem mustetext las, vnd da sprang das wort mir ins gesicht",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "wie eine flamme. Enarrant. Ich hatte narrant geschrieben.",
      "register": "mixed",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.95}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Ich bin aufgestanden. Ich bin gegangen zu dem ort, wo",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "das buch liegen sollte — es war nit mehr da. Es war fort.",
      "register": "de",
      "annotations": [{"type": "confidence", "detail": {"score": 0.97}}]
    }
  ]
}
